item.title: AS levels results
item.dc:creator: @MujaheD Radeon
item.description:
@MujaheD wrote:

I did AQA english language & literature, and for the uni I want to go to, I need to get at least a C to avoid doing a TOEFL exam (because apparently I’m studying in a non-English speaking country). I got an E on the first paper and a B on the second. It averaged out to a D… I wasn’t so happy with English, but for my other subjects I averaged out:

Math - A
Chemistry - A
Physics - B
